    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained in absolute showroom condition. This motorcar represents the pinnacle of its class, featuring an immaculate exterior finish and a pristine interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure it meets our uncompromising standards for performance and reliability. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this vehicle offers a rare opportunity to acquire a truly flawless example of automotive engineering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
